类 Selection

java.lang.Object
org.kelvinizer.constants.Selection
public class Selection extends Object
The Selection class handles the selection of collections, songs, and associated data. It stores the active collection, song, and user data, including metadata such as song jackets and score data.

This class also manages the index and directory paths for collections and songs, allowing easy navigation and retrieval of song data.
